{"tid":1237061,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"去記招既記者們","createTime":"2019-06-17T13:55:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T13:55:42.000Z","uid":5650,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ad43b2fbc4e1b3ed996e564d5b1cdad9a7ec5934","tid":1237061,"uid":5650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T13:55:42.000Z","msg":"頭先盧狗記招有感<br />\n<br />\n你地準備條發問題目可唔可以準備一下<br />\n唔係想批鬥你地 但聽到真係火火地滾<br />\n咩道唔道歉 唔洗問啦 問黎多餘<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢話連日黎得三十四宗投訴 <br />\n得一個最後先識問 但比佢走甩左<br />\n「速龍遮哂number 點投訴呀？」<br />\n呢d先係我地想關心既野<br />\n<br />\n仲有唔好噏一大堆廢話 然後先問問題<br />\n比藉口班狗話唔記得 聽唔清<br />\n問題應該簡而精<br />\n<br />\n你地係專業既 作為小市民 <br />\n希望你地可以準備下 <br />\n挫下支針 你地既問題唔夠尖銳 吉唔痛班狗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}